title: Three Seed Loaf
ingredients: ['175g (6 fl oz) water', '2 dessertspoons honey', '2 dessertspoons rapeseed oil', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '175g (6 oz) bread flour', '5 tablespoons wholemeal flour', '3 tablespoons flax seed', '2 dessertspoons sesame seeds', '1 dessertspoon poppy seeds', '1 1/4 teaspoons dried active baking yeast']
